523
01:00:23,777 --> 01:00:25,176
Vamos!

524
01:00:26,737 --> 01:00:28,216
Meu Deus!

525
01:00:41,297 --> 01:00:43,413
Vamos, depressa!

526
01:01:05,377 --> 01:01:06,571
As chaves!

527
01:01:08,377 --> 01:01:10,447
